data.description: This newly renovated four-bedroom, two-bathroom home boasts fresh paint, new flooring and doors throughout. The kitchen is beautifully remodeled with abundant cabinets, including soft-close features. Take advantage of the spacious laundry room and all of the extra closet space. This home also has an open-concept design and a separate office space. Schedule your appointment today and explore the numerous other updates.
